- Add image sizes annotation for each album item.                  <Gilles Caulier - 0.6.3>
- Added config saving of Albums opened in Albums treeview.         <Gilles Caulier - 0.6.3>
- Added dockable main widgets like Showimg.                        <Gilles Caulier - 0.6.3>
x Upload/download dynamicly the plugins.                           <Gilles Caulier - 0.6.3>
x Saving Digikam comments items in EXIF data for JPEG              <Ralf Holzer - 0.6.3>
o Custom thumbnail highlighting of album thumbnails.
o Added Albums protection with password capability.
o View/Hide main toolbar/statusbar.
o Backup and retrieve image comments and album properties.
o Add an entry 'Photo Albums' in KDEcommon FileOpen URL bar
